@jerrythornton1 Great article Jerry. One possible mistake? Francis Ouimet made Birdie on 17 in the 1913 USOPEN. 
And famous bunker is on 17, not 18. 

Curtis Strange got up and down from the green side bunker on 18 in 1988 to force an 18 hole playoff with Nick Faldo on Monday. Curtis won Bigly.
